*% ==================================================
*% ColorModel (QuadToneRIP format)
*% ==================================================
*OpenUI *ColorModel: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *ColorModel
*DefaultColorModel: QTRIP
*ColorModel QTRIP/QuadTone RIP 8-bit: "<</cupsColorSpace 1/cupsColorOrder 0/cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsBorderlessScalingFactor 1.00>>setpagedevice"
*ColorModel QTRIP16/QuadTone RIP 16-bit: "<</cupsColorSpace 1/cupsColorOrder 0/cupsBitsPerColor 16/cupsBorderlessScalingFactor 1.00>>setpagedevice"
*ColorModel QTCAL/QuadTone RIP Calibration: "<</cupsColorSpace 1/cupsColorOrder 0/cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsBorderlessScalingFactor 1.00>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *ColorModel

*% ==================================================
*% Resolution (QuadToneRIP format)
*% ==================================================
*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 2880
*Resolution 1440dpi/1440 dpi: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 1441super/1440 super: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 1442x1440dpi/1440x1440: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 1443x1440super/1440x1440 super: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2880/2880 dpi: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2881super/2880 super: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*OpenUI *ripSpeed/Speed: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *ripSpeed
*DefaultripSpeed: hispeed
*ripSpeed hispeed/Bi-directional: ""
*ripSpeed lospeed/Uni-directional: ""
*CloseUI: *ripSpeed

*OpenUI *stpDither/Dither Algorithm: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *stpDither
*DefaultstpDither: Ordered
*stpDither Ordered/Ordered: ""
*stpDither Adaptive/Adaptive Hybrid: ""
*stpDither Fast/Fast: ""
*stpDither VeryFast/Very Fast: ""
*CloseUI: *stpDither

*% ==================================================
